Package it.polimi.ingsw.core.model

Class GameState

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.core.model.GameState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class GameState extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents a GameState in the game. It maintains the player states, player order, decks, and other game-related data.
